May dump🦕

May was full of uncertainties. I planned one thing, but life had something completely different in store.
I travelled like crazy — probably more than I ever have — but strangely, didn’t enjoy any of it.
For the first time in my 25 years, I travelled alone and somehow ended up at a wedding I had sworn not to attend.
What a month. 🎢
